# ğŸ©º Kidney Disease Detection using CNN

This project implements a **Convolutional Neural Network (CNN)** to detect **Kidney Disease** from medical imaging data. The goal is to assist healthcare professionals in early detection and classification of kidney-related issues using deep learning.

---

## ğŸ“Œ Features

* ğŸ“‚ Structured ML project with modular code (config, components, utils, pipeline).
* ğŸ§  CNN-based deep learning model for disease detection.
* âš¡ Data versioning and reproducibility using **DVC**.
* ğŸ“Š Experiment tracking with **MLflow** (optional).
* ğŸš€ Ready for deployment (can be turned into an API or web app).

